definition: enemy/to be a match for/to rival/to resist/to withstand

sentences.english: The influences of semiochemicals on host selection behavior of natural enemies.
sentences.chinese: 信息化合物對天敵選擇寄主行爲的影響。

sentences.english: In eats machine in the family, the antisubmarine aircraft is submarine's natural enemy.
sentences.chinese: 在喫機家族中，反潛機是潛艇的天敵。

sentences.english: A seal body fat is one of the natural enemies of the penguins.
sentences.chinese: 體態肥碩得海豹是企鵝的天敵之一。

sentences.english: Coca Cola is an excellent rust buster.
sentences.chinese: 可口可樂是鐵鏽的“天敵”。

sentences.english: The potential of the main 3 species for biological control of Thrips palmiis is discussed.
sentences.chinese: 中華微刺盲蝽是防治節瓜薊馬前景最大的天敵之一。

sentences.english: This paper records 25 species of natural enemies of mango insect pests in Hainan Is- land.
sentences.chinese: 記錄了海南島芒果樹害蟲的天敵昆蟲25種。

sentences.english: There cattle grew wild with few natural enemies;
sentences.chinese: 那兒的牛都是野生的，基本上沒有天敵。

sentences.english: The dynamics of the natural enemy community was studied.
sentences.chinese: 研究了棉田天敵羣落時序動態。

sentences.english: Conformity and social acceptability is the natural enemy of the free mind.
sentences.chinese: 順從和社會認可是心靈自由的天敵。

sentences.english: In Hispaniola, Mr. Wilson argues, these insects had no natural enemies.
sentences.chinese: 威爾遜先生證明，這些昆蟲在海地是沒有天敵的。

sentences.english: In fact, the owl is a beneficial bird, which is the vole's natural enemies.
sentences.chinese: 其實，貓頭鷹是一種益鳥，它是田鼠的天敵。

sentences.english: Serangium japonicum is one of the important predators of Bemisia tabaci.
sentences.chinese: 日本刀角瓢蟲是粉蝨類害蟲的重要捕食性天敵之一。

sentences.english: Damage and species of natural enemies of the White Wax Insect, Ericerus pela (Chavannes) were surveyed in Kunming of Yunnan Province.
sentences.chinese: 調查了昆明地區白蠟蟲天敵種類和優勢種的危害狀況。

sentences.english: Any survivors were easy prey for predators.
sentences.chinese: 任何生還的蝗蝻都成爲天敵易於捕捉的獵物。

sentences.english: Erineum mite is a important hurtful mites attacking lychee.
sentences.chinese: 植綏蟎是控制荔枝癭蟎及其他害蟎的有效天敵。

sentences.english: The major dominant species of insect pests were Prodenia litura and Lipaphis erysimi.
sentences.chinese: 捕食性天敵主要優勢種爲八斑球腹蛛和草間小黑蛛。
